Spec for the Paragraph Element

A paragraph is a list of one or more text line elments.

They can be single line as the one above. 
Or multi-lined as this one.


1. AST

    Paragraphs are made of text lines, which them selves are made of text spans.
    Hence: 
        
		├── paragraph
		│ 	├── text-line: 
		│ 	    ├── text-span: 
        